All 32 prior findings re-confirmed against HEAD aa34d2f with anchors unchanged. Two new findings appended below: #33 PROVENANCE_INTEGRITY — promote_candidate_to_finding does not relink the trace to the new finding; the AI-proposed candidate's trace becomes invisible from the promoted finding's UI; #34 SCOPE_INVARIANT_BYPASS — list_for_candidate JOIN has no task_kind='NovelFindings' filter, so any future writer that stamps a non-NovelFindings trace_id on a candidate widens the /findings/cand-:id/traces surface to include verifier_blob and conversation_jsonl_path from arbitrary task kinds, contradicting the migration's documented intent. Total: 34 findings.

